This paper deals with mining frequent items in data streams, which is a problem that falls under the categories of databases (cs.DB) and data structures (cs.DS). The algorithm proposed in the paper involves combining ideas from several existing algorithms, which is a common approach in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses experimental results and comparisons with other algorithms, which is a common theme in information retrieval (cs.IR).
